OL,3,CMet Office confirms Thursday is the
OL,4,Chottest start to May on record
OL,6,FITV Weather Presenter Becky Mantin
OL,7,Fsays while some may celebrate the warm
OL,8,Fweather, its actually a cause for
OL,9,Fconcern.
OL,11,F"We shouldn't be getting close to 30C
OL,12,Fhere in the UK on the first of May. We
OL,13,Fshouldn't be seeing our fourth
OL,14,Fconsecutive month of below average
OL,15,Frainfall. None of this should be
OL,16,Fhappening," she said.
