OL,3,CMet Office confirms Thursday is the
OL,4,Chottest start to May on record
OL,6,F"Yes, it is lovely to have warm, sunny
OL,7,Fdays. Of course it is. But not this
OL,8,Fwarm, not this often and not this
OL,9,Fearly. Globally, 2024 was the hottest
OL,10,Fyear on record. And that should be
OL,11,Fdeeply concerning for us all."
